    <div class="card">
      <h4>Quickstart: From Idea to Action</h4>
      <ol>
        <li>Clarify the goal: what change do you want and who can deliver it?</li>
        <li>Choose tactics that fit your capacity (boycott, assembly, mutual aid).</li>
        <li>Assign roles, create safety and legal plans, and communicate clearly.</li>
        <li>Measure impact and iterate: adapt messaging and escalate responsibly.</li>
      </ol>
    </div>
